 \"from\": 551, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"the top female\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The competition bought together 28 competitors from 19 countries with strong sheep farming traditions, including Argentina, Canada, Chile, Togo, Belgium, France and the UK.\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\", \"score\": 0.999961072250794, \"rank\": 3.848287156656302e-05, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\"}, {\"begin\": 750, \"end\": 756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999992565415631, \"rank\": 7.376099997435847e-07, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.9999859122732303, \"rank\": 1.381683094337788e-05, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}, {\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Togo\", \"score\": 0.999999975215815, \"rank\": 2.4784062189983318e-08, \"text\": \"Togo\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Togo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Togo\"}, {\"begin\": 771, \"end\": 778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9999996986689893, \"rank\": 2.899176169917025e-07, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 780, \"end\": 786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999710703742606, \"rank\": 2.452213031879891e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 795, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999963051778, \"rank\": 2.492802608955428e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The competition\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 641}, {\"ngram\": \"28 competitors\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"19 countries\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"strong sheep farming traditions\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was amazing having everyone working in the same industry but in different countries,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 899, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"the same industry\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 860}, {\"ngram\": \"different countries\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are all like minded people coming together and it was incredible to achieve the results that we achieved but it was also just an amazing opportunity to meet so many great people and learn about the French culture and the industry in a different country.\\\"\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1103, \"end\": 1117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"minded people\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 931}, {\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"just an amazing opportunity\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"so many great people\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"the industry\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1134}, {\"ngram\": \"a different country\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The competition involved six tasks, all held on different farms across rural France, with the final presentation held at Bergerie Nationale in Rambouillet, an agricultural training centre and model sheep farm with a history dating back to Louis XVI.\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1238, \"end\": 1244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999710703742606, \"rank\": 2.452213031879891e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rambouillet_sheep\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4247970879531884e-20, \"text\": \"Rambouillet\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rambouillet_sheep\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rambouillet_sheep\"}, {\"begin\": 1400, \"end\": 1409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XVI\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.567976186150936e-14, \"text\": \"Louis XVI\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XVI\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XVI\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The competition\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1176}, {\"ngram\": \"six tasks\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"different farms\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"the final presentation\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"Bergerie Nationale\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"an agricultural training centre\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"model\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"sheep farm\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1369}, {\"ngram\": \"a history\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tasks included shearing, foot pairing, lamb fat scoring, drafting, a ewe health assessment and an electric fencing challenge.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The tasks\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"shearing\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"foot pairing\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"lamb fat scoring\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\": \"drafting\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"a ewe health assessment\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1506}, {\"ngram\": \"an electric fencing challenge\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Horton said judges were very particular for the foot pairing challenge.\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epsom\", \"score\": 0.9999787602137203, \"rank\": 2.1240237331315482e-05, \"text\": \"Horton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epsom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epsom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"judges\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"the foot pairing challenge\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had to make sure we were trimming the feet to the French standard,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1673, \"end\": 1679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9780370745846093, \"rank\": 0.02185662221020277, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the feet\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the ewe health assessment competitors were required to catch a ewe out of the mob and assess them from head to toe.\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases