e need to make it a really positive place to be and we need to start respecting and celebrating our farmers for the work they do to feed the country,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"young people\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3066}, {\"ngram\": \"our industry\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3092}, {\"ngram\": \"our farmers\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3201}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3214}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes agriculture is not always career path that's overly respected by the wider population and I think that needs to change.\\\"\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3387, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"agriculture\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3278}, {\"ngram\": \"career path\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3304}, {\"ngram\": \"the wider population\", \"from\": 3332, \"to\": 3352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Horton was selected to compete after being announced a 2023 Peter Westblade scholar.\", \"from\": 3389, \"to\": 3476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3392, \"end\": 3398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epsom\", \"score\": 0.9999787602137203, \"rank\": 2.1240237331315482e-05, \"text\": \"Horton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epsom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epsom\"}, {\"begin\": 3452, \"end\": 3457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spider-Man\", \"score\": 0.7754890975287949, \"rank\": 0.1824949023981541, \"text\": \"Peter\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spider-Man\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spider-Man\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Before heading to France, she spent five weeks on New Zealand's South Island visiting seven studs in the main sheep regions of Central Otago, the Marlborough, Mackenzie country and Canterbury, as part of her scholarship.\", \"from\":